Jack I know you love your job and that's so awesome, but I suggest picking a day out of the week where you don't record, upload or edit. Dedicating a day for rest from work is healthy, and helps with preventing burn out. Many "9 to 5" jobs get weekends off, and there's a good reason for that.

I hope your job remains a thing where you keep doing what you love for as long as you want! Love your energy and attitude, man.
